<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Doctor Account Credentials</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo img {
            max-width: 200px;
        }
        .content {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .credentials-box {
            background: #ffffff;
            border: 1px solid #ddd;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
        .important-note {
            color: #dc3545;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img src="<%= image_logo %>" alt="Logo">
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Welcome to Our Medical Platform</h2>
            <p>Dear Dr,</p>
            <p>Your account has been created in our medical platform. Below are your login credentials:</p>
            
            <div class="credentials-box">
                <p><strong>Email:</strong> <%= email %></p>
                <p><strong>Temporary Password:</strong> <%= password %></p>
            </div>

            <p>To access your account, please follow these steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Visit our platform login page</li>
                <li>Enter your email address</li>
                <li>Use the temporary password provided above</li>
                <li>You will be prompted to change your password upon first login</li>
            </ol>

            <p class="important-note">Important: For security reasons, please change your password immediately after your first login.</p>

            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>

            <p>Best regards,<br>The Medical Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>